sage.scene.state.jogl

Class JOGLBlendState

  • java.lang.Object
    • sage.scene.state.RenderState
      • sage.scene.state.BlendState
        • sage.scene.state.jogl.JOGLBlendState

  • public class JOGLBlendState
extends BlendState
    JOGLBlendState subclasses the BlendState using the JOGL API to set OpenGL's blending state params. This class has been modified to maintain compliance with SAGE, in regards to running on all systems using OpenGL 2.1 or newer. Blend functions and the corresponding calls to gl.glBlend will not work on systems that do not support GL2ES2
    Author:
    Mark Powell, Joshua Slack - reworked for StateRecords., Steve Vaughan - JOGL port, Jonathan Tinney - Sage port, reworked for RenderStateRecords
